tasks.task: Participate in a webinar on lentil farming
subtasks: Answer a survey about experience with lentil growing and location
Listen to Dr. Jason Brand's agronomy update
Listen to Dr. Navneet Agarwal's presentation on ryegrass management
View trial results and herbicide effectiveness for controlling ryegrass in lentils
Consider the impact of resistance development in ryegrass to different herbicide groups
Discuss the role of new herbicide Ultro in managing ryegrass in break crops
Review Dr. Jason Brand's overview of the 2018 season challenges (dry conditions, frost damage)
Evaluate variety selection considerations for 2019 (disease resistance, herbicide tolerance, soil type)
Assess the importance of seed inoculants and nutrition in lentil production
Understand market trends and pricing expectations for lentils in 2019
Examine the impact of global factors (e.g., India's tariffs) on export markets
Consider the cyclical nature of pulse market prices and production areas
Engage in question and answer session with presenters

tasks.task: Attend the GRDC funded Southern Pulse Extension project webinar to learn about lentil production and management
